platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The Montessori education method was conceptualized at the start of the 20th century by an Italian pediatrician of the same name. The idea behind it is to offer children an education based on a sensory and kinetic way of learning. Montessori Preschool is based on this ideology and provides a variety of activities, which seek to guide children ages 37 as they embark on their first steps in the world of education.

Inspired by the popular education method based on a sensory and kinetic way of learning, this app provides a variety of activities to guide children ages 37 as they embark on their first steps in the world of schooling.

En sinspirant de la populaire mthode dducation base sur un apprentissage cintique et sensoriel, cette app fournit de multiples activits pour aider les enfants gs de 3  7 ans  sadapter au milieu scolaire.
